              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "231Pa by electrodeposited on silver disks.",
                "Mass of the samples was 14.2 to 16.1 mu-g and",
                "diameter 9 mm.Subsequently the silver disks",
                "were covered with aluminium foils (34.9 mu-m",
                "thickness,99.99%, Alfa Aesar) acting as catcher",
                "foils to avoid any losses of activity by recoil",
                "processes"
              ]
